metadata.name: VOYAGE 1
metadata.description:
Created by artist and illustrator Rob Halhead. Music by SWR, London, UK. Curated by VirginiaVirtualArts. 

VOYAGE 1 is a series of unique NFTs that originated from a collaboration with artist and illustrator Rob Halhead, curator VirginiaVirtualArts and musician SWR. This NFT has a futurist approach to humankind's quest to conquer space and create a global, virtual currency.
